  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Tax Associate (Corporate/Private Client/GST)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Corporate Tax</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist and support in providing tax compliance and advisory services to clients spanning various industries</li>\n  <li>Prepare clients’ corporate and individual tax returns, including estimated chargeable income filing and withholding tax returns</li>\n  <li>Assist clients in responding to queries from the tax authorities</li>\n  <li>Attend to queries from clients and all matters arising from a portfolio of clients</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>GST</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Applying for GST registration/de-registration</li>\n  <li>Preparing, reviewing and filing GST quarterly returns</li>\n  <li>Assisting clients to apply for certain GST relief schemes</li>\n  <li>Attending to GST queries raised by IRAS</li>\n  <li>Conducting GST health checks, ASK and ACAP reviews for clients</li>\n  <li>Handling GST audits and investigations</li>\n  <li>Making voluntary disclosure of errors to IRAS</li>\n  <li>Applying for advance rulings on the GST treatment of proposed transactions</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Private Client</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist and support with tax compliance and advisory services to a portfolio of corporate, individual and trust clients</li>\n  <li>Performing tax research and analysis in the context of the private client and asset management industry and assisting with business development and networking initiatives</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preferably Degree in Accountancy or equivalent professional qualification in Accountancy or SCTP<br>\nAccredited Tax Professionals are preferred</li>\n  <li>At least 1 year of relevant experience</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude with great communication skills, meticulous, analytical and the ability to work effectively in a team</li>\n  <li>Candidate with at least 3 years of relevant experience will be considered for Senior position</li>\n  <li>Strong in written and verbal English</li>\n  <li>Good knowledge of tax laws and regulations</li>\n  <li>Good report writing and interpersonal skills</li>\n</ul>",
